<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2464] FastVectorHighlighter: add a FragmentBuilder to return entire field contents</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2464</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;In Highlightrer, there is a Nullfragmenter. There is a requirement its counterpart in FastVectorhighlighter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12464595">LUCENE-2464</key>
            <summary>FastVectorHighlighter: add a FragmentBuilder to return entire field contents</summary>
